.TH AGENT-HOOK-SESSION-START-CLAUDE 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-session-start-claude \- Claude-specific session-start adapter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-session-start-claude
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-session-start-claude
is the Claude-facing session-start entry point. It maps Claude's hook runtime
identity into AgentGuard's shared session-start behavior and emits the same
JSON response contract as
.BR agent-hook-session-start (1).
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Startup context was emitted or no context was available.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR agent-hook-session-start (1)
